title: 289. Andy & DJ CTI: FDA Restricts J&J, Misdemeanor For Chappelle's Attacker & Antifa Attacks Pregnancy Center
itunes:title: 289. Andy & DJ CTI: FDA Restricts J&J, Misdemeanor For Chappelle's Attacker & Antifa Attacks Pregnancy Center
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the FDA restricting the Johnson & Johnson Covid-19 vaccine due to blood cloth risks, the Los Angeles District Attorney's office's decision to not bring felony charges against Dave Chappelle's onstage attacker, and Antifa's attack on a pregnancy center in Portland.
